						"title": "Build and host your own site using AI vibe coding",
						"titleSize": null,
						"subtitle": null,
						"subtitleSize": null,
						"copy": "With the recent AI-powered \"vibe coding\" boom, you can build a website or application by simply describing what they want in a few sentences…and see your code generated in a few minutes. Cloudflare has all the tools to help you manage your site, from start to finish.  \n\n- Take your code and deploy it seamlessly to Cloudflare's serverless network with one click. \n- Secure a custom domain for your project using Cloudflare's Registrar across over 400 top-level domains (TLDs) at wholesale pricing - you pay what Cloudflare pays. \n- Enroll in Cloudflare's Free Plan that includes security and performance tools, such as a free SSL/TLS certificate, ultra-fast DNS, a global CDN, and comprehensive DDoS protection.\n",
