						"contentfulId": "72LJwyxG3zhusGXQnkjyZF",
						"title": null,
						"copy": "<p> <span style=\"font-size:32px;line-height:120%;\"> <strong>Code, Build, and Deploy Easily and Quickly</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"> By using Cloudflare's vibe coding AI tool,  anyone can create their own site quickly and easily to deploy and host it across Cloudflare's network.</span></p>\n\n- First, enter your prompt on what you'd like to build\nat [build.cloudflare.dev](https://build.cloudflare.dev/).  \n- Watch the code being generated for your project in real-time along with a front-end preview.\n- Adjust to your preferences using the AI chat feature. \n- Hit the __Deploy__ button in the top-right corner to launch your project on Workers.\n\n*What is a Cloudflare Worker?*\n<br>A worker is like a robot that runs that runs and makes decisions based on your program or code everywhere on Cloudflare's global network, making them fast",
