						"title": null,
						"copy": "<p> <span style=\"font-size:32px;line-height:120%;\"> <strong>Secure a Custom Domain for your Project and Connect Your Code</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span></p>\n\n- If you don't yet have a domain, [search for your intended domain](https://domains.cloudflare.com/) on the Cloudflare Registrar, and pay for at-cost pricing with no markups, year-after-year. \n- Cloudflare Registrar supports over 400 top-level domains (TLDs), including .ai, .io, .biz, .dev, and more. View the [full list](https://domains.cloudflare.com/tlds) of supported extensions. \n- Connect your new Workers in your Cloudflare dashboard under __Workers & Pages__. Select your worker and add your custom domain under the Worker Settings (Domains & Routes).\n",
